{"tid":764302,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］有冇咩背囊好介紹？","createTime":"2018-08-02T00:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T15:50:26.000Z","uid":47671,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"22a10a15351d39470d92ed5c87c17ec12f41f9f1","tid":764302,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:24:26.000Z","msg":"其實我想知有咩牌子，嚟嚟去去都係Outdoor 呢啲其實仲有冇其他你地覺得係好，我知有個香港品牌冬甩，但我想知仲有咩。<br />\n<br />\n我其實本身睇中一個英國牌子Chrome，但問題個運送過程麻煩，一嚟佢都唔係平，二嚟運費又貴變相成件事就麻煩，不過真係幾靚係不錯的又岩踩車。<br />\n<br />\n我預計如果香港有好背囊我預算1000蚊到啦，再貴啲都可以。<br />\n<br />\n我用途都係返學，返工最好可以咩嚟踩車就十分好，不過我想要個夠大，多格數，Chrome個啲功能性好正又防水，但真係運送過程鳩Kick。<br />\n<br />\n所以想集思廣益睇吓其實背囊有咩牌子係好嘅，比到多啲選擇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b418cf36922165b55d7f4b5578fea438efc6869f","tid":764302,"uid":8867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69644ef5173fd7be2917e801b11250ad3177d0d5","tid":764302,"uid":129120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"Gregory"},{"pid":"3cfcd920bdb31dd38e5442f33e9406028d353b97","tid":764302,"uid":47671,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b418cf36922165b55d7f4b5578fea438efc6869f","tid":764302,"uid":8867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:37:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"呢個好撚MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周街都係"},{"pid":"ad7bc9741e0f111b235cec672a55436140328c38","tid":764302,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:44:44.000Z","msg":"咪又係herschel eastpak Jansport Fj&auml;llr&auml;ven vans，基本上香港人咩開個啲都包曬喺度"},{"pid":"ab037ed036868c4a49529307348a1e0b400fc2ba","tid":764302,"uid":47671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":